                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9685" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1455</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1319 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“卖风机”到“卖生态”：金风科技绿色低碳转型的破局之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From &quot;Selling Wind Turbines&quot; to &quot;Selling Ecology&quot;: Goldwind&#39;s Breakthrough Road to Green and Low-Carbon Transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">林红珍，冯锦熙</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆金风科技股份有限公司 </td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金风科技；“五位一体”；资源编排理论；价值链；循环经济协同效应</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Goldwind Technology; &quot;Five-in-One&quot;; Resource Orchestration Theory；Value Chain；Synergy in Circular Economy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在“双碳”目标驱动下，国家正加速推进绿色低碳发展，制造业面临迫切的转型升级需求。本案例聚焦于全球风电巨头金风科技，描述了其如何依托自身资源优势，紧密结合下游用户需求，成功实现从传统风机制造商向绿色低碳生态型企业的转型。金风科技通过实施技术创新、构建绿色供应链管理体系、推行全生命周期设计理念、推进智能化生产以及提供零碳解决方案等“五位一体”的转型措施，不仅促进了自身的绿色低碳转型，还通过示范项目引领行业向零碳方向迈进。金风科技成为行业内唯一的国家标准验证点，并成功打造了国内首个零碳园区示范项目，实现了从“卖风机”到“卖生态”的战略升级。本案例适用于管理会计相关课程的教学，旨在引导学生从战略高度理解绿色低碳转型的价值创造逻辑，培养其将可持续发展理念融入管理决策的专业能力，对于培养具有环保责任感的管理会计人才具有重要教育意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> Driven by the &quot;dual carbon&quot; goal, the country is accelerating green and low-carbon development, and the manufacturing industry is facing urgent needs for transformation and upgrading. This case study focuses on Goldwind, a global wind power giant, and describes how it has successfully transformed from a traditional wind turbine manufacturer to a green, low-carbon and ecological enterprise by relying on its own resource advantages and closely integrating the needs of downstream users. Through the implementation of technological innovation, the construction of a green supply chain management system, the implementation of the whole life cycle design concept, the promotion of intelligent production, and the provision of zero-carbon solutions, Goldwind has not only promoted its own green and low-carbon transformation, but also led the industry to move towards zero-carbon through demonstration projects. Goldwind has become the only national standard verification point in the industry, and has successfully built the first zero-carbon park demonstration project in China, realizing the strategic upgrade from &quot;selling wind turbines&quot; to &quot;selling ecology&quot;. This case is applicable to the teaching of management accounting related courses, aiming at guiding students to understand the value creation logic of green and low-carbon transformation from a strategic perspective, and cultivating their professional ability to integrate the concept of sustainable development into management decisions, which is of great educational significance for cultivating management accounting talents with environmental responsibility.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色供应链理论；资源编排理论；价值链理论；价值创造理论；循环经济协同效应理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-07</td>
                            </tr>
